            </configure>
        </apply>
        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>To standardize parts on International steer axles, straight tie rod ends and a new tie rod tube
                    are now available for discontinued axle codes 02337(SBA) and 02343, with drop tie rod ends.
                </para>
                <para>Use of the new (standardized) tie rod ends and tie rod tube on the 02337(SBA) and 02343 axles
                    requires removal of the tie rod arms (lower steering arms) and re-installation of the arms on the
                    opposite knuckle.
                </para>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
